                                    <div class="text-wrapper">
                                        <p class="title">Rethinking the GMP: Turning cost certainty into clarity</p>
                                        <div class="excerpt-wrapper"><p>A GMP doesn’t create clarity, it reflects it. Align scope and assumptions early to reduce risk and improve outcomes.</p>
</div>
